name: MindSeat
description: We rent office equipment to digital nomads in Bali. We aim to have 30% APR for our investors. We want to raise 50 ETH (as an angel investment for %5 of $SEAT). We will use the funds for a trial run of 20 setups, build a social media following around it and set the company for scaling towards a goal of 1000 desk setups by Dec 2022.
